    "Query designOur query development process involves breaking down the study subject into a few key phrases.",
    "Then we attempted other combinations of synonymous words to those phrases.",
    "There were a total of three segments in our search query.",
    "First, we included the search phrase \"Artificial Intelligence\" in the initial segment of our query.",
    "We also included similar terms such as \"AI\", \"ML\", and \"Machine Learning\" in that portion."
